                  <join result="persNamePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17291015-80-defend455 t17291015-80-defloc388"></join>, was indicted for <rs id="t17291015-80-off389" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17291015-80-off389" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17291015-80-off389" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing a Gold Watch, Chain, and two Seals, in the Dwelling-House of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17291015-80-victim437" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Stibbs 
                        <interp inst="t17291015-80-victim437" type="surname" value="Stibbs"></interp>
