            , was likewise indicted for stealing the said Watch; but no Evidence appearing against her, she was <rs id="t17291015-80-verdict393" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17291015-80-verdict393" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17291015-80-verdict393" type="verdictSubcategory" value="noEvidence"></interp>
